TopicTitle: Does Distant Objects work with latest version?

Articles.Content: I can't seem to get it to work. I see that the mod author is no longer updating it. Did someone pick it up and update it for the latest version? I mainly want it for the darker skies. After using it for so long the default sky with all the stars looks ridiculous.
Thank you so much! I tried to play without it last night and I just couldn't do it.
